It's just a fun thing to do.

00:11:07.867 --> 00:11:10.503 line:95%,end
And it's a fresh new take
on your choreography.

00:11:10.569 --> 00:11:12.571 line:95%,end
And it gives the children
an opportunity

00:11:12.638 --> 00:11:14.607 line:95%,end
to dance with somebody
other than you.


