I'm here with the fabulous ladies
of the show

00:11:17.309 --> 00:11:20.046 line:95%,end
who make it happen every week,
make it so exciting.

00:11:20.112 --> 00:11:23.749 line:95%,end
So Kelly, I have a question
with you and Abby.

00:11:23.816 --> 00:11:26.752 line:95%,end
You guys have a long history together.

00:11:26.819 --> 00:11:28.554 line:95%,end
You guys have known each other
for a very long time...

00:11:28.621 --> 00:11:30.089 line:95%,end
-ABBY: Yes.
-JEFF: ...since you were what, two?

00:11:30.156 --> 00:11:31.590 line:95%,end
