00:11:43.869 --> 00:11:44.904 line:95%,end
mad at me,

00:11:45.805 --> 00:11:47.139 line:95%,end
holds a grudge against me.

00:11:47.206 --> 00:11:49.075 line:95%,end
I don't know
if it's because I quit dance.

00:11:49.141 --> 00:11:50.976 line:95%,end
