00:11:51.043 --> 00:11:53.412 line:95%,end
she liked a guy, and he liked me.
I mean, there was--

00:11:53.479 --> 00:11:55.047 line:95%,end
She was 12, and he was 18, so--

00:11:55.114 --> 00:11:57.750 line:95%,end
-JEFF: Did she steal your boyfriend?
-I was not 12, but--

00:11:57.817 --> 00:11:59.151 line:95%,end
Did you steal her boyfriend?

00:11:59.218 --> 00:12:00.820 line:95%,end
No, he wasn't my boyfriend.

00:12:00.886 --> 00:12:01.987 line:95%,end
-No, it wasn't her boyfriend.
-JEFF: All right.

00:12:02.054 --> 00:12:03.622 line:95%,end
