00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:09.395 line:95%,end
Ah!

00:12:09.462 --> 00:12:10.863 line:95%,end
Jill Vertes!

00:12:10.930 --> 00:12:12.064 line:95%,end
No, I didn't.

00:12:12.131 --> 00:12:14.600 line:95%,end
No, but seriously, there's a lot
of tension between you two.

00:12:14.667 --> 00:12:16.235 line:95%,end
And we see it.
It goes--it goes a long way.

00:12:16.302 --> 00:12:18.104 line:95%,end
I--I want to know about it. Tell me.

00:12:18.871 --> 00:12:20.973 line:95%,end
