No, not at all.

00:12:24.877 --> 00:12:26.345 line:95%,end
JEFF: So where does this tension
come from?

00:12:27.947 --> 00:12:30.583 line:95%,end
Don't forget, I was 14
when I started my company.

00:12:30.649 --> 00:12:32.752 line:95%,end
