the mom's dance.

00:12:39.859 --> 00:12:42.228 line:95%,end
Stop. I didn't feel...

00:12:42.294 --> 00:12:44.296 line:95%,end
that your mom and dad pushed you

00:12:44.363 --> 00:12:46.365 line:95%,end
the way they should have.

00:12:46.432 --> 00:12:48.901 line:95%,end
I think I've done pretty well
for myself

00:12:48.968 --> 00:12:50.536 line:95%,end
without my parents pushing me.

00:12:50.603 --> 00:12:51.937 line:95%,end
-And...
-KELLY: I did what I wanted to do.

00:12:52.004 --> 00:12:54.240 line:95%,end
