-KELLY: I wanted to get married.

00:12:54.306 --> 00:12:55.407 line:95%,end
I wanted to have kids.

00:12:55.474 --> 00:12:57.042 line:95%,end
I wanted to be a stay-at-home mom.

00:12:57.109 --> 00:12:58.244 line:95%,end
