00:13:25.771 --> 00:13:28.207 line:95%,end
...is born with a God-given talent

00:13:28.274 --> 00:13:30.009 line:95%,end
that you should encourage it.

00:13:30.075 --> 00:13:31.210 line:95%,end
You should push it.

00:13:31.277 --> 00:13:32.778 line:95%,end
You should make it available to them.

00:13:32.845 --> 00:13:35.381 line:95%,end
But my kid was born
with a God-given talent.

00:13:35.447 --> 00:13:37.149 line:95%,end
-And she did win all your titles...
-ABBY: Right.

00:13:37.216 --> 00:13:39.451 line:95%,end
...and everything just like Maddie did.
