and knocking her down.

00:13:42.621 --> 00:13:43.823 line:95%,end
And now, she doesn't want
to dance anymore.

00:13:43.889 --> 00:13:45.491 line:95%,end
And that's the same thing
that happened with me

00:13:45.558 --> 00:13:47.259 line:95%,end
