And Brooke wants to do other things.

00:14:06.278 --> 00:14:08.013 line:95%,end
And that's why I'm giving her
the opportunity.

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:09.748 line:95%,end
So Kelly, let me--
let me ask you a question.

00:14:10.482 --> 00:14:12.484 line:95%,end
At--at nationals, you--

00:14:12.551 --> 00:14:14.119 line:95%,end
you had a meltdown.

00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:15.821 line:95%,end
It's hard to watch your kids on stage

00:14:15.888 --> 00:14:18.224 line:95%,end
and think it's the last time
you're gonna watch them dance.


