00:14:32.338 --> 00:14:34.306 line:95%,end
I mean, when Brooke tells me that...

00:14:34.373 --> 00:14:36.342 line:95%,end
she just wants to be
with her friends and wants to--

00:14:36.408 --> 00:14:38.043 line:95%,end
I mean, I understand it.
I went through it.

00:14:38.110 --> 00:14:39.578 line:95%,end
I'm not going to force them to dance

00:14:39.645 --> 00:14:41.714 line:95%,end
for the rest of their life
if that's not what they want.

00:14:41.780 --> 00:14:44.083 line:95%,end
Then why force me to give them...

00:14:44.149 --> 00:14:45.885 line:95%,end
