00:15:06.538 --> 00:15:07.706 line:95%,end
or Brooke's better than me.

00:15:07.773 --> 00:15:09.208 line:95%,end
-Like...
-But when is it going to click in...

00:15:09.275 --> 00:15:10.876 line:95%,end
...why do you think
they even want that?

00:15:10.943 --> 00:15:12.544 line:95%,end
...and they're gonna say,
