for them yet. Maybe...

00:15:16.882 --> 00:15:18.417 line:95%,end
-ABBY: Right.
-...it has for somebody else.

00:15:18.484 --> 00:15:20.286 line:95%,end
-Right, maybe it hasn't.
-Every kid is different.

00:15:20.352 --> 00:15:22.021 line:95%,end
