00:15:22.087 --> 00:15:24.223 line:95%,end
After teaching kids for that long,

00:15:24.290 --> 00:15:27.359 line:95%,end
you don't understand
that every single child

00:15:27.426 --> 00:15:28.894 line:95%,end
-in this world is different.
-ABBY: I understand that.

00:15:28.961 --> 00:15:30.129 line:95%,end
